sequenceDiagram
    participant Visitor
    participant Frontend
    participant API
    participant DB
    participant SMS as AWS SNS

    Visitor->>Frontend: Enter Phone Number
    Frontend->>API: POST /public/visitors/send-otp
    API->>DB: Store OTP (expiry 5m)
    API->>SMS: Send OTP
    SMS-->>Visitor: Receive SMS (e.g. "123456")
    
    Visitor->>Frontend: Enter OTP
    Frontend->>API: POST /public/visitors/verify-phone
    API->>DB: Validate OTP & Attempt Count
    
    alt OTP Valid
        API-->>Frontend: Success + Visitor Profile (if exists)
        Frontend->>Visitor: Show Registration Form (Prefilled/Empty)
    else OTP Invalid
        API-->>Frontend: Error (Invalid/Expired)
        Frontend->>Visitor: Retry Message
    end
